      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 142</em>, <em>PRPG Core Rulebook pg. 469</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> moderate evocation <strong>CL</strong> 8th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> weapon quality; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>Upon command, a <em>frost </em>weapon is sheathed in a terrible, icy cold that deals an extra 1d6 points of cold damage on a successful hit. The cold does not harm the wielder. The effect remains until another command is given.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>chill metal </em>or <em>ice storm</em>; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
